channel.title: How come some .exe progs dont work?
channel.description:
[center]Some of the .EXE programs don't work on my computer, well this is what happened, they worked perfectly but then I saved all my stuff in this flash drive, then my dad rebooted the computer and I reinstalled them and they don't work, like runescape autominer, and even if I download different stuff with .exe it does'ny want to work!!
Please help, it would mean alot to me..[/center]
